edu.harvard.integer.access.snmp

Class SnmpService

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.access.snmp.SnmpService

  • public final class SnmpService
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class SnmpService is an singleton class to provide SNMP communication service. It also contains methods for different type of SNMP requests.
